This paper describes a deep reinforcement learning approach for generalizing and adapting to unseen environments in the context of man-made environments. The paper focuses on visual navigation tasks using House3D, a 3D environment that contains diverse human-designed indoor scenes with real-world objects. Given the focus on deep reinforcement learning, computer vision, and robotics, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, and cs.CL.
